message.text:
Great Efforts, Real Impact 👣

Puksaan here, puksaan there, puksaan everywhere? True the fire! But hey, trust me, it's so worth it! Messages like this one keeps us going and it reminds us of what we're really here for: to serve the IABF community to the best of our abilities. 🫶🏻

We are looking for like-minded individuals who share the same passion as ours. If you're more than ready to make real change in the institute, then STRAW Internal Affairs is the one for you!

From drafting petition letters, to attending to student concerns every semester, to submitting consolidated student grievances reports and crafting resolutions, we've done it all. With YOU, we will continue to be the bridge between the student body and the institute this year.

Come and join FEU IABF Student Council and be a part of the STRAW Internal Affairs Division. We're already waiting for you. 🥹
